[
  {
    "startTime": 19.9,
    "endTime": 23.334999999999997,
    "text": "Jesteros needs a new king or queen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.335,
    "endTime": 27.8,
    "text": "And I decide we will play a game-- a Game of Chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.8,
    "endTime": 28.8,
    "text": "Huzzah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.8,
    "endTime": 34.8,
    "text": "And here to tell you how to play the game is Grover Bluejoy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.8,
    "endTime": 36.73,
    "text": "Grover Bluejoy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.73,
    "endTime": 38.099999999999994,
    "text": "Where is Grover Bluejoy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.1,
    "endTime": 41.5,
    "text": "Sorry I'm late, but it was really hard getting over that wall out there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.5,
    "endTime": 43.4,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.4,
    "endTime": 46.35,
    "text": "Just tell everyone how to play the game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.35,
    "endTime": 47.6,
    "text": "Aye-t."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.6,
    "endTime": 52.561,
    "text": "The Game of Chairs is played with a deck of cards."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.561,
    "endTime": 53.31,
    "text": "No, it's not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.31,
    "endTime": 56.14,
    "text": "Of course it does not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.14,
    "endTime": 57.9,
    "text": "Who said that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.9,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "The Game of Chairs is played with marbles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 60.9,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.9,
    "endTime": 65.5,
    "text": "The monster is blue and full of errors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.5,
    "endTime": 66.7,
    "text": "Is it played with a rubber chicken?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.7,
    "endTime": 69.21000000000001,
    "text": "NO!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.21,
    "endTime": 75.80999999999999,
    "text": "The Game of Chairs is played with chairs, these three chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.81,
    "endTime": 78.2,
    "text": "You know, that makes sense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.2,
    "endTime": 82.69,
    "text": "But what do you do with the chairs?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.69,
    "endTime": 85.1,
    "text": "Music will play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.1,
    "endTime": 93.8,
    "text": "And then, these four players who want to be king or queen will march around these three chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.8,
    "endTime": 99.7,
    "text": "When the music stops, they will each try and sit in a chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.7,
    "endTime": 102.8,
    "text": "The lucky players who sit in a chair will--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.8,
    "endTime": 106.8,
    "text": "Will have a nice, comfy place to rest their cute and weary bodies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.8,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Oh, I love this game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.1,
    "text": "NO!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.1,
    "endTime": 115.19999999999999,
    "text": "They will continue to compete to be the king or queen until there is one chair left."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.2,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "That is the Game of Chairs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Huzzah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 120.35,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.35,
    "endTime": 122.8,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.8,
    "endTime": 125.7,
    "text": "You were supposed to bring the music, Bluejoy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.7,
    "endTime": 128.1,
    "text": "Right, right, right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.1,
    "endTime": 130.1,
    "text": "Be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.1,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 139.26,
    "text": "Stop the music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.26,
    "endTime": 140.1,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.1,
    "endTime": 141.9,
    "text": "I said, stop the music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.9,
    "endTime": 144.3,
    "text": "Sorry, I cannot tell you over this music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.3,
    "endTime": 149.10000000000002,
    "text": "Stop the MUSIC!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.1,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Oh--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 155.7,
    "text": "Oh, my baby's sad because we lost."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.7,
    "endTime": 159.32,
    "text": "Aw, I am sorry little-- whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.32,
    "endTime": 163.5,
    "text": "A mommy of dragons?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.5,
    "endTime": 169.74,
    "text": "No need to get hot under the diaper."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.74,
    "endTime": 171.24,
    "text": "So how many players are left?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.24,
    "endTime": 173.35000000000002,
    "text": "Let us count."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.35,
    "endTime": 180.262,
    "text": "We have one, two, three players, and one, two, three chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.262,
    "endTime": 182.22,
    "text": "Three chairs and three players."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.22,
    "endTime": 183.5,
    "text": "- Got it. - Can we hurry this up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.5,
    "endTime": 185.2,
    "text": "I have a wedding to get to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.2,
    "endTime": 185.66,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.66,
    "endTime": 186.29999999999998,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.3,
    "endTime": 187.8,
    "text": "Remove one of the chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.8,
    "endTime": 188.9,
    "text": "Ah, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.9,
    "endTime": 195.5,
    "text": "Removing one of the chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.5,
    "endTime": 199.2,
    "text": "Sorry about the floor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.2,
    "endTime": 206.2,
    "text": "Now, there are one, two chairs left, and three players."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.2,
    "endTime": 208.5,
    "text": "Let's continue the game."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.5,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 211.66,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 219.2,
    "text": "Stop the music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.2,
    "endTime": 220.58999999999997,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.4,
    "endTime": 226.12,
    "text": "Stop the music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.12,
    "endTime": 227.8,
    "text": "Whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.8,
    "endTime": 229.20000000000002,
    "text": "Am I out?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.2,
    "endTime": 230.29999999999998,
    "text": "Yes, I am sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.3,
    "endTime": 235.305,
    "text": "It looks like you choked, Joffrey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.305,
    "endTime": 236.8,
    "text": "So how many players are left?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.8,
    "endTime": 238.72,
    "text": "Let us count."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.72,
    "endTime": 241.0,
    "text": "There are one, two players."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.0,
    "endTime": 241.7,
    "text": "Two players."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.7,
    "endTime": 243.546,
    "text": "And one, two chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.546,
    "endTime": 244.79999999999998,
    "text": "Two chairs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.8,
    "endTime": 246.8,
    "text": "Now, remove one more chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.8,
    "endTime": 252.4,
    "text": "Ah, removing one more chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.4,
    "endTime": 256.19,
    "text": "We really should get some wheels on these things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.19,
    "endTime": 259.69,
    "text": "That leaves one chair and two players."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.69,
    "endTime": 266.2,
    "text": "The one person to sit in this one chair will be the next king or queen of Jesteros."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.2,
    "endTime": 267.518,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.518,
    "endTime": 273.46999999999997,
    "text": "Music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.47,
    "endTime": 275.3,
    "text": "And stop the music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.3,
    "endTime": 276.446,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.446,
    "endTime": 280.20000000000005,
    "text": "Stop the music!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.2,
    "endTime": 281.09999999999997,
    "text": "Ow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.1,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "Ow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 286.8,
    "text": "There is one chair, and only one person can be in that chair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.8,
    "endTime": 290.8,
    "text": "And that person is--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.8,
    "endTime": 292.17,
    "text": "Hello."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.17,
    "endTime": 293.0,
    "text": "You?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.0,
    "endTime": 295.4,
    "text": "I'm telling my brother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.4,
    "endTime": 296.67999999999995,
    "text": "You're the new king?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.68,
    "endTime": 300.56,
    "text": "I cannot think of a more horrible ending than this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.56,
    "endTime": 306.33,
    "text": "All hail King Grover."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.33,
    "endTime": 308.09999999999997,
    "text": "Nice fit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.1,
    "endTime": 310.20000000000005,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.2,
    "endTime": 313.42199999999997,
    "text": "Do not lose your head over this, Neddie, baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.422,
    "endTime": 316.0,
    "text": "Now, fetch me a cushion for my royal bottom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.0,
    "endTime": 317.4,
    "text": "This chair is not comfy at all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.4,
    "endTime": 320.76,
    "text": "Yes, your fuzzy grace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.76,
    "endTime": 322.26,
    "text": "And bring a sweater."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.26,
    "endTime": 331.5,
    "text": "I think winter is coming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.5,
    "endTime": 345.6,
    "text": "He says, \"then I'll huff and I'll puff and I'll blow your house down!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.6,
    "endTime": 347.96000000000004,
    "text": "A thing of beauty."
  }
]